# OpenSpec + Git (LSI)

**Canonical overlay:** [`.lsi/workflows/openspec-git-integration.md`](../../.lsi/workflows/openspec-git-integration.md)

OpenSpec changes under `openspec/changes/<change-slug>/` define **what to build**. Trello + branch id define **delivery tracking**.

**Branch policy:** [`.cursor/rules/branch-workflow.mdc`](branch-workflow.mdc) — do not duplicate protected-branch refusal here.

## Workflow commands

**OpenSpec:** `/opsx:explore`, `/opsx:propose`, `/opsx:apply`, `/opsx:sync`, `/opsx:archive`

**LSI (git):** `/lsi:card`, `/lsi:branch`, `/lsi:senior`, `/lsi:commit`, `/lsi:readiness`, `/lsi:review`, `/lsi:pr`, `/lsi:promote`, `/lsi:merge-desc`, `/lsi:close`, `/lsi:version`, `/lsi:changelog`, `/lsi:release`, `/lsi:bootstrap-release`

| Step | Command |
|------|---------|
| Explore | `/opsx:explore` |
| Propose | `/opsx:propose` |
| Card + branch | `/lsi:card` (from `main`) |
| Senior analysis | `/lsi:senior` (large changes) |
| Implement | `/opsx:apply` |
| Commit | `/lsi:commit` (when asked) |
| Pre-PR | `/lsi:readiness` → `/lsi:review` |
| PR to staging | `/lsi:pr` |
| Promote to main | `/lsi:promote` (after staging QA) |
| Merge desc | `/lsi:merge-desc` |
| Release | `/lsi:version`, `/lsi:changelog`, `/lsi:release`, `/lsi:bootstrap-release` |
| Close | `/lsi:close` on **`main`** (after promotion) |

## Before implementation

1. Confirm ticket branch with Trello id + OpenSpec slug suffix.
2. Read `proposal.md`, `design.md`, delta specs for active change.
3. **`tasks.md` must not** list `/opsx:sync`, `/opsx:archive`, or `/lsi:close` — production-close steps on **`main`** via `/lsi:close`, not `/opsx:apply` deliverables.

## Commits and PRs

- On commit requests: `/lsi:commit` — plan from `tasks.md` sections.
- On PR prep: `/lsi:readiness` then `/lsi:review` before `/lsi:pr`.
- PR **Related:** `openspec/changes/<slug>/` + Trello card id.
- Do not auto-commit or auto-open PRs.
- When policy is ambiguous, ask one focused question before proceeding.

See [openspec-git-integration.md § Full lifecycle](../../.lsi/workflows/openspec-git-integration.md).
